message.body: Later this evening Going to take kids to pool for about 30 minutes or so. Would Paige want to come?
She had a busy day & Richard is taking her fishing tomorrow, so we are hoping for an earlier night???!!!
Ok-she would probably love it, since we have been asked 5x about the pool today!
We were going about 6:30 or 6:45 and only 30 minutes cuz Alex has a game in the morning. We are not staying long since it will be cold if that would change your mind.
I'll let you know when we get home and are getting ready. If Shantel is home, she is welcome to come also
Getting ready and be down when done
